Package cetus.hir

Class IDExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • cetus.hir.Expression
      • cetus.hir.IDExpression
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Printable, Traversable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<Expression>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DestructorID, Identifier, NameID, OperatorID, QualifiedID, TemplateID
    public abstract class IDExpression
extends Expression
    IDExpression represents an IR object that appears as an identifier in the program. In C programs, only the two child classes of IDExpression, NameID and Identifier, are used.
